query:
INSERT INTO projectMembers (projectId, userId, role) 
SELECT p.id, 1, 'owner' 
FROM projects p 
WHERE p.archivedAt IS NULL 
AND NOT EXISTS (
  SELECT 1 FROM projectMembers pm 
  WHERE pm.projectId = p.id AND pm.userId = 1
);
